
           Commands available from the Alias Menu in Elm 2.3

 Key    Meaning
 ---    -------

  ?     Help on a specific key, or this summary of commands.

  a     Add the return address of current message to alias database, (or
        the regular address if current message is copy of a message sent).

  d     Delete a user alias from alias database.

  l     List all aliases in the database.

  m     Make a new user alias, adding it to alias database when done.

  r,x   Return from the alias menu.

  p     Check for a person in the alias database.

  s     Check for a system in the host routing/domain database.
